{
  "stem": "16106.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had quite a few of German [GERMAN] someone, someone were old, some were young.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was a long table where we ate our bread at night.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't get much extra stuff there, that we had to live on our rations, more or less.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were two things which happened there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There, not far from there, was a factory for, for beets, where they made sugarcane.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there was something dripping out the pipes which was, which was sweet and brown.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We collected that in tins and put it on our bread.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was-- still remember that smell.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That's what we got there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it was clean.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then one day I got a cockamamie idea.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I will never eat-- I will not eat for four days, my rations, and then eat it, the whole lot on once-- at once.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "When I went to look for it, it was gone.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Learned my lesson.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I always had the instinct to-- in the morning, you get up, you brush your teeth, you comb your hair, and you wash yourself.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It's concentration camp or not, I did that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we didn't have much water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We had ice.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So I used to kick the ice and take the ice and wash myself.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And one morning-- I, I remember that, that, that we had appell and that Austrians, somebody or other, or [INAUDIBLE] said, you should all take as an example of number so-and-so, which was me, washes self-- herself every morning with ice to stay clean and, and, and healthy.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because if you do not stay clean, you may get sick.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when you are sick, we will have to send you back to Stutthof, and you know what that means for you.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see that?",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
